<doc id="113416" wikidata="Q7785625" url="?curid=113416" title="This Broken Heart">
<text>This Broken Heart may refer to several songs:

* &quot;This Broken Heart&quot; (1959), from American Doo Wop vocal quintet The Sonics
* &quot;This Broken Heart&quot; (1973), from American funk band Funkadelic&#x27;s album &quot;Cosmic Slop&quot;, a cover version of The Sonics&#x27; original.
* &quot;This Broken Heart&quot; (2003), from California rock band Something Corporate&#x27;s album &quot;North&quot;
* &quot;This Broken Heart&quot; (2006), from New Zealand rock band Tadpole&#x27;s album &quot;Tadpole&quot;</text><links>
<link wikidata="Q2998281" start="228" end="239" title="Cosmic Slop" label="Cosmic Slop"/>
<link wikidata="Q975277" start="398" end="403" title="North (Something Corporate album)" label="North"/>
